GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-aid-freeze-disrupts-anti-narcotics-program-mexican-ports-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国的Shimao以11美元的近海债务改造获得了债权人的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-secures-creditor-backing-11-bln-offshore-debt-revamp-2025-02-24/</link><description>中国房地产开发商Shimao集团已确保债权人的支持，以重组约110.4亿美元的离岸债务，这是多年的流动性麻烦之后，该行业的最新交易。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 11:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-secures-creditor-backing-11-bln-offshore-debt-revamp-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国的习近平在乌克兰战争周年纪念日中与普京的“无限制”伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-hold-phone-call-ukraine-war-anniversary-state-media-says-2025-02-24/</link><description>中国媒体在与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）的电话中，在俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰的三周年纪念日报道，中国总统习近平在与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的电话中确认了他的“无限制”伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 10:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-hold-phone-call-ukraine-war-anniversary-state-media-says-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/illegal-us-vape-sales-worth-least-24-billion-2024-data-shows-2025-02-24/</link><description>根据路透社审查的私人零售销售数据，美国未经授权的一次性一次性vapes的销售额约为2024年的24亿美元，或者来自诸如便利店和超市等商店的电子烟的35％。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 10:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/illegal-us-vape-sales-worth-least-24-billion-2024-data-shows-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>CATL的大众汽车在中国合作开发锂电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-catl-collaborate-china-lithium-battery-development-2025-02-24/</link><description>CATL周一说，大众集团的中国子公司和全球最大的电池制造商CATL计划合作开发大众汽车在中国电动汽车的锂电池。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 09:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-catl-collaborate-china-lithium-battery-development-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>骗局中心镇压之后，泰国山区边界上的数千人处于困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-limbo-thai-myanmar-border-after-scam-centre-crackdown-2025-02-24/</link><description>三名消息人士周一告诉路透社，成千上万的外国人从缅甸的在线骗局运营中心被释放在与泰国边界的边界上，在对犯罪团伙经营的化合物的跨国镇压之后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-limbo-thai-myanmar-border-after-scam-centre-crackdown-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>国家以2000亿美元的自然金融协议进行新的尝试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/countries-make-fresh-attempt-200-billion-nature-finance-deal-2025-02-24/</link><description>本周的各国聚集在罗马，第二次裂开，弄清楚如何每年产生2000亿美元以帮助维护世界的生物多样性 - 并随着美国的回归而射击全球合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/countries-make-fresh-attempt-200-billion-nature-finance-deal-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>购买饮食以创建欧洲食品的“冠军”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/prosus-buy-just-eat-takeawaycom-create-european-food-delivery-firm-2025-02-24/</link><description>它周一说，荷兰技术投资者已同意以41亿欧元（43亿美元）的价格购买Out Out Takewaway.com，以创建“欧洲科技冠军”的粮食交付。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 06:23:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/prosus-buy-just-eat-takeawaycom-create-european-food-delivery-firm-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>晨价：当德国投票躲避极端时，救济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-02-24/</link><description>看看韦恩·科尔（Wayne Cole）的欧洲和全球市场前一天。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 05:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰外交大臣质疑北京访问中国海军活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-foreign-minister-question-chinese-naval-activity-beijing-visit-2025-02-24/</link><description>新西兰的外交部长温斯顿·彼得斯（Winston Peters）将于周二在北京进行为期三天的访问，因为两国之间的关系在中国海军船只在塔斯曼海进行了现场射击演习后紧张。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 04:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-foreign-minister-question-chinese-naval-activity-beijing-visit-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示，它分享了日本反对单方面尝试重塑全球秩序的事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-it-shares-japans-cause-opposing-unilateral-attempts-reshape-2025-02-24/</link><description>其国防部长周一说，菲律宾与日本有任何单方面试图重塑全球秩序的共同原因。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-it-shares-japans-cause-opposing-unilateral-attempts-reshape-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>铁矿石因中国钢的更多职责而升高为期四天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/iron-ore-snaps-four-day-rise-due-more-duties-chinese-steel-2025-02-24/</link><description>达利安铁矿石期货价格在周一取得了为期四天的连胜纪录，因为中国钢铁的征收增加了主要的钢材制造成分的需求前景，尽管中国的港口库存减少了秋季。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/iron-ore-snaps-four-day-rise-due-more-duties-chinese-steel-2025-02-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>